2017年3月6日，[[翠西·梅丹朵芙|翠西·梅丹朵芙]]在推特上宣佈她將不會回歸參演第三季，<ref>{{cite tweet |number=838964146225864704 |title=Won't be back for @MTVScream 3. Thanks to the amazing fans for supporting the show & actors.@willafitz @IBexWeBex @johnny_k @FollowCarlson |date=2017-03-06 |access-date=2017-03-19 |user=tracymiddendorf |last=Middendorf |first=Tracy}}</ref>而其他主演也隨著第三季的重啟而將不會回歸劇組。<ref name="Season 3"/>

2017年7月17日，宣布饒舌歌手兼演員{{le|泰加 (藝人)|Tyga|泰加}}與{{le|克里斯托佛·喬丹·華萊士|Christopher Jordan Wallace|C·J·華萊士}}加入第3季主演陣容，分別飾演賈莫與阿米爾。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tyga-cj-wallace-star-rebooted-scream-season-3-1021559|title=Tyga, C.J. Wallace to Star in Rebooted 'Scream' Season 3 (Exclusive)|publisher=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|author=Lesley Goldberg|date=2017-07-17|accessdate=2017-07-17|archive-date=2017-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717193626/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tyga-cj-wallace-star-rebooted-scream-season-3-1021559|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月13日，宣布《[[尖叫女王|尖叫女王]]》{{le|琪琪·帕瑪|Keke Palmer}}（飾演姬姆）、《[[含笑上台|含笑上台]]》[[RJ·賽勒|RJ·賽勒]]（飾演迪昂）、《[[漢娜的遺言_(電視劇)|漢娜的遺言]]》{{le|喬治雅·維格罕|Giorgia Whigham}}（飾演貝絲）、《{{le|康復之路|Recovery Road (TV series)}}》{{le|潔西卡·蘇拉|Jessica Sula}}（飾演莉芙）與《{{le|茱莉的小舞台|Julie's Greenroom}}》{{le|裘力安·姚·祖利耶洛|Giullian Yao Gioiello}}（飾演梅尼）加入第3季主演陣容。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/keke-palmer-star-scream-season-3-mtv-1037710|title=Keke Palmer to Star in 'Scream' Season 3 for MTV (Exclusive)|publisher=好萊塢報導|author=Lesley Goldberg|date=2017-09-13|accessdate=2017-09-14|archive-date=2017-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914000719/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/keke-palmer-star-scream-season-3-mtv-1037710|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 評價 ==
《驚聲尖叫》獲得了影評家好戶參半的評價。於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得了47%的新鮮度、5.36/10分（30位評論家），評論家共識：「缺乏真正引人注目的角色與場景，《驚聲尖叫》硬是依賴著大銀幕系列前作的懷舊來作消費。」<ref>{{cite web|title=Scream: Season 1|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/scream/s01/|publisher=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2018-01-31|archive-date=2017-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203155807/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/scream/s01/|dead-url=no}}</ref>第2季獲得100%新鮮度、7.5/10分（5位評論家）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Scream: Season 2|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/scream/s02/|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2018-01-31|archive-date=2017-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128052656/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/scream/s02/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得57分（滿分100分；20位評論家），屬好壞參半的評價。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/scream-2015|title=Scream (2015) - Season 1 Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2018-01-31|archive-date=2018-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214192623/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/scream-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>

